SELECT "company_name"."country_code", "movie_companies"."company_type_id", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "movie_companies" LEFT OUTER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "title"."id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_info_idx" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info_idx"."movie_id"  WHERE CAST("company_type"."kind" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%compani%es%' GROUP BY "company_name"."country_code", "movie_companies"."company_type_id" ORDER BY "company_name"."country_code", "movie_companies"."company_type_id";
SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, min("name"."imdb_id" + "name"."id") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "name"  WHERE CAST("name"."name" AS varchar) LIKE '%All%en,%';

SELECT "title"."imdb_index", "title"."series_years", min("movie_companies"."company_id") as agg_0, max("movie_companies"."id" + "title"."episode_nr") as agg_1 FROM "company_name" LEFT OUTER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "company_name"."id" = "movie_companies"."company_id" LEFT OUTER JOIN "title" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "title"."id"  WHERE CAST("company_name"."name" AS varchar) LIKE '%The%' GROUP BY "title"."imdb_index", "title"."series_years" ORDER BY "title"."imdb_index", "title"."series_years";
